        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 1. — Graphicomassa Iredale, 1929 lectotypes and paralectotypes: A-F, Columbella ligula Duclos, 1840: A-E, match Duclos’ (1840) figures: A, Lectotype, MNHN-IM-2000-22712, Philippines, 19.3 mm; B, MNHN-IM-2000-22711, Philippines, 18.4 mm; C, MNHN-IM-2000-22709, Seychelles, 16.6 mm; D-E, MNHN- IM-2000-22710, I. Nevis (err), 17.0 mm, 16 mm respectively; F, MNHN-IM-2000-22709, Seychelles, 15.7 mm; G-H, Columbella albina Kiener, 1841, Locality unknown:G, Lectotype,MNHN-IM-2000-22472-1. 14.85 mm;H, Paralectotype,MNHN-IM-2000-22472-2. 16.3 mm; I-J, Columbella adiostina Duclos,1840. Locality unknown: I, Lectotype, MNHN-IM-2000-6332-1, 14.3 mm; J, Paralectotype, MNHN-IM-2000-6332-3, 12.05 mm Photos taken by MNHN. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4578052/files/figure.png" .

